oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Samuel D. Milliken genealogical information
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Samuel D. Milliken genealogical information. Samuel was the father of James Alexander "Alec" Cathey Milliken. James Milliken recorded the genealogy and it is in his handwritting. James Alexander "Alec" Cathey Milliken (April 3, 1836-September 20, 1920), Co. K, 1st Tenn. Inf. (Turney's) Regt., CSA. He was detailed as a medical sergeant under Dr. Calvin McGuire and worked in this capacity during the Second Battle of Manassas.
